readme.text:
TgKit

## About > [!WARNING] > **This library is under development!** It doesn't yet cover Telegram Bot API 100% and may contain bugs. Library API may change at any time. Use it in production at your own risk. > **None of the code is generated**. Every type and structure is hand-written, hence there can be some mistakes. Please open an issue if you find any! TgKit is library for interacting with [Telegram Bot API](https://core.telegram.org/bots/api) ### Features * Lightweight * Object-oriented, has predictable abstractions and [Typescript](https://typescriptlang.org/) type defentitions included ## Example
